## RESTORATION INSTRUCTIONS

If you need to restore any archived files:

### From master_plan/archive/:
```powershell
Copy-Item master_plan\archive\<filename> master_plan\
```

### From specs/archive/:
```powershell
Copy-Item specs\archive\<filename> specs\
```

### From .meta/archive/:
```powershell
Copy-Item .meta\archive\PATCH_PLAN_JSON\<filename> PATCH_PLAN_JSON\
Copy-Item .meta\archive\patches\<filename> patches\
```

### To regenerate build artifacts:
```bash
# Regenerate coverage reports
pytest tests/ --cov=core --cov-report=html

# Coverage files will be recreated automatically
```
